# Once done this will define
#
#  FFmpeg_FOUND - system has ffmpeg or libav
#  FFMPEG_INCLUDE_DIR - the ffmpeg include directory
#  FFMPEG_LIBRARIES - Link these to use ffmpeg
#  FFMPEG_LIBAVCODEC
#  FFMPEG_LIBAVFORMAT
#  FFMPEG_LIBAVUTIL
